  "detailed_description": "\"回家 - Homeward\" a relaxing puzzle game, Follow a team of Leopard Cat, black bears and monkeys, native to Taiwan, as they lead you on an adventure from the city to the mountains, exploring Taiwan together and bringing back scenes you may have seen before in your memory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.poster.avif?t=1652942157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.webm?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.mp4?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=== Game Features ===</h2> - Various scenes in picture book style to explore all parts of Taiwan.<br><br> - The role of animals unique to Taiwan and getting to know protected species.<br> - Various puzzles and interesting mechanisms, a challenge to think big.<br> - Simple and clear click operation, easy to enjoy the game.<br> - Fresh and lovely game content, no horror and violence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.poster.avif?t=1652942157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.webm?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.mp4?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"回家 - Homeward\" a relaxing puzzle game, Follow a team of Leopard Cat, black bears and monkeys, native to Taiwan, as they lead you on an adventure from the city to the mountains, exploring Taiwan together and bringing back scenes you may have seen before in your memory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.poster.avif?t=1652942157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.webm?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/e0cb179a59d50e86093594deafaedd9d.mp4?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=== Game Features ===</h2> - Various scenes in picture book style to explore all parts of Taiwan.<br><br> - The role of animals unique to Taiwan and getting to know protected species.<br> - Various puzzles and interesting mechanisms, a challenge to think big.<br> - Simple and clear click operation, easy to enjoy the game.<br> - Fresh and lovely game content, no horror and violence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.poster.avif?t=1652942157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.webm?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757950/extras/ea4c001dc7fcb9130f027f90db66514f.mp4?t=1652942157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
